(61, 'Best Dental Implants in Guntur: The Permanent Solution for Missing Teeth By Dr. Abhilash', NULL, '<p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">What Are Dental Implants?&nbsp;</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dental implants are advanced tooth replacement solutions that mimic the natural tooth structure. They consist of a titanium post surgically placed in the jawbone, acting as an artificial root, and a crown that restores functionality and aesthetics. Unlike dentures or bridges, </span><a href=\"https://visiondentalguntur.com/implants.php\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">full mouth dental implants in Guntur</a><a href=\"https://visiondentalguntur.com/implants.php\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">provide a long-term and stable solution for missing teeth, making them one of the most sought-after treatments at our hospital.</span></p><p><br></p>', NULL, '<p><br></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Why Are Dental Implants Used?&nbsp;</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dental implants are used to replace missing or damaged teeth due to various reasons such as tooth decay, injury, or gum disease. They restore chewing ability, improve speech, and enhance facial aesthetics. Additionally, implants prevent bone loss by stimulating the jawbone, maintaining its structure and strength. At </span><a href=\"https://visiondentalguntur.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Vision Multi Specialty Dental Hospital</a><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">we provide</span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/8dJxwdF\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"> </a></strong><a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/8dJxwdF\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">affordable dental implants in Guntur</a><a href=\"https://visiondentalguntur.com/implants.php\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">to ensure everyone has access to quality treatment.</span></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Benefits of Dental Implants&nbsp;</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">Durability</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: With proper care, dental implants can last a lifetime.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">Natural Appearance</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Implants look and feel like natural teeth.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">Improved Chewing &amp; Speech</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: They function like real teeth, allowing for better eating and speaking abilities.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">Bone Preservation</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Prevents bone loss that occurs with missing teeth.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">No Damage to Adjacent Teeth</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">:</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Unlike dental bridges, implants do not require altering neighboring teeth.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">Painless Dental Implants in Guntur</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">:</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> With advanced technology, dental implant surgery is now minimally invasive and virtually painless.</span></li></ol><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Importance of Dental Implants</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Missing teeth can lead to shifting of remaining teeth, jawbone deterioration, and aesthetic concerns. </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Permanent teeth replacement in Guntur</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> through dental implants helps maintain facial structure, preventing premature aging caused by bone loss. They also boost confidence and overall oral health, making them an essential solution for tooth loss. If you are searching for the </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">best dentist for dental implants near me</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, our specialists at Vision Multi Specialty Dental Hospital are here to help.</span></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Types of Dental Implants&nbsp;</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">Endosteal Implants</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: The most common type, placed directly into the jawbone.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">Subperiosteal Implants</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">:</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Positioned under the gum but above the jawbone, suitable for patients with insufficient bone.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">Zygomatic Implants</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">:</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> A less common type, anchored in the cheekbone for severe bone loss cases.</span></li></ol><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Precautions &amp; Measures Before and After Dental Implants&nbsp;</strong></h3><h4><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">Before the Procedure:</strong></h4><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Maintain good oral hygiene and treat any existing gum disease.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Follow the dentist’s instructions regarding medications and diet before surgery.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Avoid smoking and alcohol consumption to ensure better healing.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Undergo necessary X-rays and CT scans to assess bone density.</span></li></ol><h4><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(71, 126, 7);\">After the Procedure:</strong></h4><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Follow a soft food diet for a few days to prevent pressure on the implant site.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Maintain oral hygiene with gentle brushing and prescribed mouthwash.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Avoid smoking, as it can delay healing and increase the risk of implant failure.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Attend regular dental check-ups for proper implant maintenance.</span></li></ol><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Best Dental Hospital for Implants in Guntur&nbsp;</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">At </span><a href=\"https://visiondentalguntur.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Vision Multi Specialty Dental Hospital&nbsp;Guntur</a><a href=\"https://v