es. A </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">balanced diet</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> rich in vitamins and minerals strengthens enamel, prevents gum disease, and supports long-term dental health.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">4. What is the best way to take care of permanent teeth?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Maintain </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">regular brushing, flossing, and dental check-ups</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">. Pair this with a </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">nutrient-rich diet</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> and avoid excessive sugary foods. For advanced care, consult specialists in </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">permanent teeth treatment in Guntur</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> at Vision Multispeciality Dental Hospital.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">5. Why should I choose Vision Multispeciality Dental Hospital?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We are known as the </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">best dental hospital in Guntur</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> with highly skilled specialists like </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dr. Abhilash Naik</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> and </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dr. Latha Sree</strong><span style=\"background-color: tr