(134, 64, 'Michael', 'michaelbjones648@gmail.com', 'I got infected with genital herpes (HSV2) from group sex party 6 years ago \r\nI started taking lysine 3000 mg of lysine once a day and it worked well for me during outbreaks but it was not enough for me as it does not stop it from breaking out anytime without warning. I endured this for years.\r\nThe fear of a future outbreak made me look for an alternative and I was directed to try Dr Utu Herbal Cure. \r\nAmazingly, it worked so well for me, I can\'t believe it \r\nDr Utu Herbal Cure completely cured me hsv2 and I have stayed up to two years with no outbreaks and no side effects from even treatment. It\'s been life changing. \r\nIf you still suffering contact him at \r\ndrutuherbalcure@gmail.com', NULL, NULL, '2026-01-01 16:50:16', 1, 0),
(135, 64, 'Taylor M Redden', 'taylormredden@gmail.com', 'I was diagnosed with HSV2 in my eye and mouth from semen. I had no idea regretfully that it could be transferred through semen on your face. As I suffered two weeks of continuous pain and rash in the right eye and mouth suspecting herpes then I went to run a test and was diagnosed with hsv2. It was then that I realized it had finally gotten to me despite how much I have always tried to play safe. I started taking lysine and supplements except valtrex because I heard that I can’t get off without having nonstop outbreaks if I take valtrex. A month later I included acyclovir eye drops and pain killer and many other herpes treatment I can get then to prevent blindness. I tried everything for two years to cure myself but to no tangible results . I became worried and afraid of losing eyesight and also my hearing since I was told that herpes can travel from your eye to the ears. \r\nI can\'t bear the thought of losing an eye and my hearing because of my ignorance which has already begun affecting my mental health. I encouraged myself and started attending seminars and anything that could help with my mental health. During this period someone I called God sent saw the sores and recognised it was a herpes infection. She told me that Dr Utu herbal cure had cured her when she was in a similar situation to me. I became interested and she gave me his email address drutuherbalcure@gmail.com. I contacted Dr Utu who assured me that after treatment there will be no more herpes in my body. In good faith, I decided to give him a trial for the sake of my mental health. He prepared me four weeks herbal treatment that permanently cured me. I have done HSV test to be sure and the result came out negative.  I am living my life without any fear of losing my eyesight or hearing.\r\nNo more depression or anxiety I have gotten back my life with Dr Utu Herbal Cure and I feel much satisfied 💯', NULL, NULL, '2026-01-01 16:51:27', 1, 0),
(136, 64, 'Shirley Murray', 'shirleymurray3041@gmail.com', 'I have had 4 sexual partners in 30 years including a 25 year marriage. Then luckily met a wonderful man both he and I have a strong attraction to one another and under normal circumstances would probably have sex daily. I value our relationship and we decided to be sexually monogamous and also decided to get routine STD tests. To my astonishment and horror my results were that I had antibodies for HSV2.\r\nI have never ever had an outbreak of genital herpes, but have read about shedding. The idea of using drugs daily is not good for me, it was a nightmare. Even though he had promised to always stand by me and that hsv2 would never come in between us I was still not satisfied. We decided to work this out together, and I am happy about that but not comfortable because I would wish for him to feel protected. The pressure on my head forced me to start searching for blogs and forums to see if anyone has ever been completely cured. Then I started seeing testimonies of people who have claimed herbal medicine cured their herpes. Among them all Dr Utu Herbal Cure got my attention and I decided to give him a first trial before checking another, lo and behold he was my last. His herbal medicine cured me and when I went for another test I was tested hsv2 negative. Anyone going through Hsv2 can contact Dr Utu at drutuherbalcure@gmail.com', NULL, NULL, '2026-01-01 16:53:09', 1, 0),
